{"tid":272710,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"德國港生點燭光悼六四","createTime":"2017-06-06T04:39:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-06T04:40:13.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c02917ab88a454ff315ba578f3e8422698bfb7fb","tid":272710,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T04:39:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20045950&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170606\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20045950%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170606&d=mlgTEEQq0fcbdNU03PtHEBv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=dc16e84e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20045950%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170606&h=97c37c31\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20045950&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170606</a><br />\n<br />\n德國港生點燭光悼六四<br />\n<br />\n要聞&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n9名香港學生於布蘭登堡門悼念六四，吸引不少人圍觀。 互聯網<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】9名在德國讀書的香港學生於當地六四晚上，自發到柏林布蘭登堡門悼念六四，包括默哀、點蠟燭、宣讀當年學運領袖的絕食宣言，高峯時逾百人圍觀。<br />\n參與的港生葉沛瑜指，德國人及在德的外籍學生，一般對六四不了解，或只覺得中國強大，她認為有關活動可建立平台讓德國人了解真實的中國。<br />\n葉與8名在德國留學的友人在柏林悼念六四，因布蘭登堡門象徵着1989年時柏林圍牆倒下，有歷史意義，故選擇到該處悼念。她指活動吸引不少人駐足，「原來好多德國人對中國人權狀況唔了解」。<br />\n其間，葉遇上專程坐5個小時火車到布蘭登堡門、「碰運氣」悼念六四的港生。為使悼念薪火相傳，葉指已有同學接棒，決定明年舉行集會，將真相流傳。<br />\n■記者廖梓霖<br />\n<br />\n97年主權移交至今，香港前進還是倒退？「蘋果」與你細數廿載風雨。<br />\n【回歸二十年】專頁：&nbsp;<a href=\"http://hksar20.appledaily.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhksar20.appledaily.com.hk&d=mlgTEEQq0fcbdNU03PtHEBv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=a047d2f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hksar20.appledaily.com.hk</a>￼<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n何俊仁斥學生口吻如董建華<br />\n<br />\n要聞&nbsp;6小時前<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n湯家驊：六四非鄰國歷史<br />\n<br />\n要聞&nbsp;6小時前<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n支聯會籌款少去年30萬<br />\n<br />\n要聞&nbsp;6小時前<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n現屆：集體悼念要停　舊生：傳承歷史有責中大學生會　兩代會長拗六四分歧<br />\n<br />\n要聞&nbsp;6小時前"},{"pid":"74c727a651c76357d504498bfea1c36130e23bcf","tid":272710,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T04:40:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170606/large/a0604a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170606%2Flarge%2Fa0604a.gif&h=38462a78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n9名香港學生於布蘭登堡門悼念六四，吸引不少人圍觀。 互聯網<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}